### Elasticsearch SQL - Tüm Tabloları Göster
POST http://localhost:9200/_sql?format=json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SHOW TABLES"
}

### Elasticsearch SQL - Content-Index'ten Veri Çek
POST http://localhost:9200/_sql?format=json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SELECT * FROM \"content-index\" LIMIT 10"
}

### Elasticsearch SQL - Koşullu Sorgulama
POST http://localhost:9200/_sql?format=json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "SELECT title, score FROM \"content-index\" WHERE score > 8.0 ORDER BY score DESC"
}

### Elasticsearch REST - Tüm Dokümanlar
GET http://localhost:9200/content-index/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": {
    "match_all": {}
  },
  "size": 20
}

### Elasticsearch REST - Arama
GET http://localhost:9200/content-index/_search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": {
    "match": {
      "title": "test"
    }
  }
}

### Elasticsearch - Index İstatistikleri
GET http://localhost:9200/content-index/_stats

### Elasticsearch - Cluster Sağlık
GET http://localhost:9200/_cluster/health?pretty